    <title>Olivia Rodrigo – you seem pretty sad for a girl so in love</title>
    <link>https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/olivia-rodrigo-you-seem-pretty-sad-for-a-girl-so-in-love/</link>
    <guid isPermaLink="true">https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/olivia-rodrigo-you-seem-pretty-sad-for-a-girl-so-in-love/</guid>
    <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 04:03:00 +0000</pubDate>
    <enclosure url="https://media.pitchfork.com/photos/6a1064f4cdd971dc49dbe97b/16:9/w_1280,c_limit/Olivia%20Rodrigo%20-%20You%20Seem%20Pretty%20Sad%20for%20a%20Girl%20So%20in%20Love%20album%20art%20(no%20sticker).png" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>The pop star’s third album is a heartbreaking account of an intense romance and its demise. Its mood is perfectly reflected in the music, and her evolution as a songwriter is a sight to behold.</p>
<img src="https://media.pitchfork.com/photos/6a1064f4cdd971dc49dbe97b/16:9/w_1280,c_limit/Olivia%20Rodrigo%20-%20You%20Seem%20Pretty%20Sad%20for%20a%20Girl%20So%20in%20Love%20album%20art%20(no%20sticker).png" alt="you seem pretty sad for a girl so in love cover"/>
