    <description><![CDATA[<p>On its latest album, the prolific Welsh duo takes a warped view of human anatomy in a set of twee-pop and post-punk songs free of innuendo and laced with feral enthusiasm.</p>
<img src="https://media.pitchfork.com/photos/6a22f1b3bb3dc604ca9365f2/16:9/w_1280,c_limit/The%20Bug%20Club-Every%20Single%20Muscle.png" alt="Every Single Muscle cover"/>
